	</text>
	<text id="nav_text" x="207" y="425" width="564" height="" autosize="H" style="PROMPT" visible="false" fx="PROMPT_SHOW" hidefx="PROMPT_HIDE">
		<content translate="true">Click a &lt;B&gt;Lesson&lt;/B&gt; or &lt;B&gt;Activity &lt;/B&gt;to learn more about &lt;B&gt;Why Stress Matters&lt;/B&gt;.</content>
	</text>
	<section id="presentation_text" align="LEFT" spacing="0x10" autospace="true" columns="0" exclusive="false" expanded="true">
		<text id="text01" x="350" y="60" width="395" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="true" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Many parents wonder what happens if their child is stressed for an extended period of time. </content>
		</text>
		<text id="text02" x="350" y="85.2" width="380" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">While the optimal scenario is to identify the stressor and make a repair attempt, or teach the child techniques for managing stress, sometimes the situation is beyond the parent or child's control. In these instances, the support and care of a trusted adult is the best buffer against the negative effects of stress. </content>
		</text>
		<text id="text03" x="350" y="85.2" width="380" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Romanian Orphanages Research Spotlight:</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text04" x="350" y="114.8" width="395" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;LI&gt;The longer the children lived in these conditions, the less well-regulated their stress response system was.&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text05" x="350" y="160" width="395" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;LI&gt;Children who had alternating caretakers and who had been in the orphanage for longer than six months demonstrated lower cognitive scores.&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text06" x="350" y="160" width="395" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;LI&gt;The longer the child had lived in the institution, the more slowly the ability to regulate stress occurred.&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
	</section>
